<subSubSection id="F3AEBE7776F16BF02AF4AB7972BEADED" pageId="null" pageNumber="393" type="nomenclature">
<paragraph id="DB79CE77D6623C9FB94FCD9749E13EAB" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">
<taxonomicName id="9CC0F60B055BAF2D40CBC36C1054EA2E" authority="Colla" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Campanulaceae" genus="Campanula" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="393" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="bertolae">
Campanula 
<normalizedToken id="610159B69589861FCB2210C07B05EA60" originalValue="Bértolae" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">Bertolae</normalizedToken>
Colla
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="888E37980BF543F95AAA21DC35E63FCD" pageId="null" pageNumber="393" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="E748C3ADFB7518CF95CBE02DB37861C8" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">Bertolas Glockenblume</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="EED284EA336090C16D99087D6E9ACED4" pageId="null" pageNumber="393" type="description">
<paragraph id="EF62762A88C1462A115991AE0E60F92C" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">
15-40 cm hoch, meist ohne sterile Blattrosetten. Rhizom dick, verholzt. Stengel aufrecht oder bogig aufsteigend, 
<emphasis id="D3A0E7F48D82BE62300591543D1EF370" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">auch im untern Teil meist kahl</emphasis>
oder dann ganze Pflanze behaart. 
<emphasis id="1F3FE29DBE4AC44FE010B1974CF6F1D2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">
Untere 
<normalizedToken id="832D92434D07083184F27A2BF5902C54" originalValue="Stengelblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">Stengelblaetter</normalizedToken>
ganzrandig, sehr schmal lanzettlich, kaum breiter als 2 mm und 20
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="0D9418A1B35D8861B15564658FBFEEE3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">40mal so lang wie breit</emphasis>
, kahl. 
<normalizedToken id="D70EFAD0A5784AF553DAF0A2354AAC6A" originalValue="Blüten" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">Blueten</normalizedToken>
in einer lockeren Traube, aufrecht oder nickend. 
<normalizedToken id="11B2435BD2F83C6D73CDB98A141BBA23" originalValue="Blütenknospen" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">Bluetenknospen</normalizedToken>
aufrecht. Kelchzipfel 
<normalizedToken id="89EE5B3F20EB9BF4624CCFEF157AF0C5" originalValue="höchstens" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">hoechstens</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="FC528ECCAD2239D08BAD8051B32AD159" originalValue="½" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">1/2</normalizedToken>
so lang wie die Krone, aufrecht. Krone 
<normalizedToken id="1EB32D76F83FF0FE04310138758AF3CE" originalValue="glockenförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">glockenfoermig</normalizedToken>
, 1-2 cm lang, blauviolett. - 
<normalizedToken id="DE5A35FE0952312B82416FF81F00758F" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="201B8AA03AEF227BB7D2EF97FA66D6C5" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">
<emphasis id="428FBB14A6F1E8D0E3A8B3DB1B313504" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="BDC98C95D37ED081028C40BF9F8E1A7A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">102:</emphasis>
Material aus der Provinz Torino (Podlech und Damboldt 1963).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7F408A4658E7BAB93FC02CD22DB028F3" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">
<emphasis id="0BCB129FB571F3E823334346F701C04B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">Standort.</emphasis>
Montan, seltener kollin oder subalpin. Kalkarme, humose 
<normalizedToken id="04E388B96943BB008349F8AA8501600E" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in 
<normalizedToken id="698F8AA9C1DE24696F35C39674F6EC6E" originalValue="wärmeren" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">waermeren</normalizedToken>
Lagen. Lichte 
<normalizedToken id="CEA7503E71F5AFE11E3E10C810C12ECA" originalValue="Kastanienwälder" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">Kastanienwaelder</normalizedToken>
, 
<taxonomicName id="D5529FCF2F8DDCBC6F6738796472E274" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ericaceae" genus="Calluna" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="null" pageNumber="393" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="59F618F6179E4435AC5A10E809805E66" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">Calluna</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
heiden, 
<emphasis id="30F8EF5683B845BC1188785661A9751A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">Nardusweiden.</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C9F591D9536B1D7D14DC770B64F073BC" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">
<emphasis id="BD692500684F518C837D680677374259" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="1BE929223913BE695675ED7FF36786D3" originalValue="Südalpin-apenninische" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">Suedalpin-apenninische</normalizedToken>
Pflanze:
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="51511FCEECDC2FC98D3954553B2F54B6" originalValue="Südliche" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">Suedliche</normalizedToken>
Alpen vom Monte Baldo 
<normalizedToken id="919F859C65DB5EE6746F701123B96433" originalValue="westwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">westwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis zu den Seealpen; Apennin (
<normalizedToken id="105C001FFEF263B27E63E72188FA02E0" originalValue="südwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">suedwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Abruzzen und Campania). - Im Gebiet: Gegend von Varese, 
<normalizedToken id="B6BE31D585B722B03A0C5D60AA5FF104" originalValue="südliches" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">suedliches</normalizedToken>
Tessin, Comerseegebiet.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A7EB4034273E055F04A2E923B50C268B" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">
<emphasis id="A611BA389B7A5767C90CC55588F50AEA" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">Bemerkungen.</emphasis>
Nach Podlech (1965) kommt die Art nur in den italienischen 
<normalizedToken id="562F381AD818F6FC7FAF415A576E038F" originalValue="Südwestalpen" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">Suedwestalpen</normalizedToken>
vor. Die 
<normalizedToken id="73C4BF05F91DA32A287685C233135CA6" originalValue="Identität" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">Identitaet</normalizedToken>
der insubrischen Sippe 
<normalizedToken id="40C7ADF9DABB16FDA80AE3130A1A784D" originalValue="muß" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">muss</normalizedToken>
deshalb 
<normalizedToken id="E198BB3215184CB1488E061CCD6EE081" originalValue="abgeklärt" pageId="null" pageNumber="393">abgeklaert</normalizedToken>
werden.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
